Interface SizedIterable<T>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements held by this iterable.
All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:
Bag<Item>
All Known Implementing Classes:
Bag_Array, Queue_Elements, SizedIterableImpl
public interface SizedIterable<T> extends Iterable<T>
The SizedIterable interface provides a contract for iterables with a defined size and additional utility methods for convenience. This interface extends the standard Iterable interface, ensuring that any implementation is iterable while also providing methods to determine the size of the collection and convert it to a List.
